<% content_for :title, "HoneyOps Pricing | Trial and Per-Honeypot Plans" %>
<% content_for :meta_description, "HoneyOps pricing is simple: 1 trial honeypot for 30 days, then 15 €/month per active honeypot with a 3-honeypot minimum, including full platform capabilities." %>

<div class="min-h-screen bg-slate-950 text-slate-100">
  <%= render "main/site_header", active: :pricing %>

  <main>
    <section class="border-b border-slate-900 bg-slate-950 py-16">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6">
        <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl text-center">
          <div class="mb-2 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-amber-400">Pricing</div>
          <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-slate-100 sm:text-5xl">
            Straightforward pricing that scales with your deployment
          </h1>
          <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-slate-300">
            Start with a full-featured trial and move to predictable per-honeypot billing with a simple minimum commitment.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="border-b border-slate-900 bg-slate-950 py-16">
      <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-5xl gap-6 px-6 md:grid-cols-2">
        <article class="relative rounded-3xl border border-amber-500/60 bg-amber-500/10 p-8 shadow-sm">
          <div class="absolute -top-3 left-8 rounded-full bg-amber-500 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold text-slate-950 shadow">
            30-day trial
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <div class="inline-flex rounded-xl bg-amber-500/15 p-3 text-amber-300">
              <%= honey_icon(:shield, classes: "h-6 w-6") %>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-100">Trial honeypot</h2>
              <p class="text-sm text-slate-300">Best for evaluation and internal validation.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="mt-6 flex items-baseline gap-1">
            <span class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-amber-300">0 €</span>
            <span class="text-slate-400">for 30 days</span>
          </div>

          <ul class="mt-6 space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-300">
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><%= honey_icon(:shield, classes: "h-4 w-4 text-amber-400") %><span>1 active honeypot</span></li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><%= honey_icon(:activity, classes: "h-4 w-4 text-amber-400") %><span>30-day evaluation period</span></li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><%= honey_icon(:server, classes: "h-4 w-4 text-amber-400") %><span>OVA or Windows deployment mode</span></li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><%= honey_icon(:bell, classes: "h-4 w-4 text-amber-400") %><span>Email notifications and policy controls</span></li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><%= honey_icon(:ticket, classes: "h-4 w-4 text-amber-400") %><span>Basic email support</span></li>
          </ul>
        </article>

        <article class="rounded-3xl border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900 p-8 shadow-sm">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <div class="inline-flex rounded-xl bg-amber-500/15 p-3 text-amber-300">
              <%= honey_icon(:server, classes: "h-6 w-6") %>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-100">Production plan</h2>
              <p class="text-sm text-slate-300">Best for continuous protection in live environments.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="mt-6 flex items-baseline gap-1">
            <span class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-amber-300">15 €</span>
            <span class="text-slate-400">per honeypot / month</span>
          </div>
          <ul class="mt-6 space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-300">
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><%= honey_icon(:shield, classes: "h-4 w-4 text-amber-400") %><span>Minimum contract: 3 honeypots</span></li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><%= honey_icon(:activity, classes: "h-4 w-4 text-amber-400") %><span>Continuous production use</span></li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><%= honey_icon(:server, classes: "h-4 w-4 text-amber-400") %><span>OVA or Windows deployment mode</span></li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><%= honey_icon(:bell, classes: "h-4 w-4 text-amber-400") %><span>Email notifications and policy controls</span></li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><%= honey_icon(:ticket, classes: "h-4 w-4 text-amber-400") %><span>Email support for live environments</span></li>
          </ul>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="bg-slate-950 py-16">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-6 text-center">
        <p class="text-sm leading-7 text-slate-300">
          Billing is straightforward: after the 30-day trial, active honeypots are billed at 15 € per month,
          with a minimum contract volume of 3 honeypots. Trial and production deployments follow the same
          operational workflow, and partner or high-volume terms can be discussed case by case.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-5 text-sm leading-7 text-slate-300">
          Planning a larger rollout across many sites? Contact
          <a href="mailto:info@honeyops.net" class="font-semibold text-amber-400 hover:underline">info@honeyops.net</a>.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <%= render "main/site_footer" %>
</div>
